---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about Dalmatia Estates - over a decade of curating exceptional Croatian villa experiences">
  <header class="page-header">
    <span class="page-header__tag">Our Story</span>
    <h1 class="page-header__title">A Decade of Croatian Excellence</h1>
    <p class="page-header__desc">
      Founded in 2014, Dalmatia Estates has become the trusted name in luxury 
      Croatian villa rentals, serving discerning travelers from around the world.
    </p>
  </header>
  
  <section class="about-intro">
    <div class="about-intro__image">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555990538-1e7a7210d4c3?w=1200&q=85&auto=format" alt="Croatian coastline" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-intro__content">
      <h2>Passionate about <em>Croatia</em></h2>
      <p>
        Our journey began with a simple belief: that Croatia's extraordinary coastline 
        deserves to be experienced in equally extraordinary accommodations. What started 
        as a small collection of three villas in Dubrovnik has grown into a curated 
        portfolio of over 48 exceptional properties along the Dalmatian Coast.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every estate in our collection has been personally visited and vetted by our 
        team. We look beyond the obvious—seeking properties with soul, history, and 
        that ineffable quality that transforms a vacation into a cherished memory.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="values">
    <div class="values__header">
      <span class="values__tag">Our Values</span>
      <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="values__grid">
      <div class="value">
        <span class="value__num">01</span>
        <h3>Curated Excellence</h3>
        <p>We say no more often than we say yes. Only properties that meet our exacting standards join the collection.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <span class="value__num">02</span>
        <h3>Personal Touch</h3>
        <p>Every guest is assigned a dedicated concierge who knows Croatia intimately and anticipates your needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <span class="value__num">03</span>
        <h3>Local Expertise</h3>
        <p>Our team lives and breathes Croatia. We share hidden gems, local connections, and insider experiences.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <span class="value__num">04</span>
        <h3>Seamless Service</h3>
        <p>From your first inquiry to your farewell, every detail is handled with precision and care.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="team">
    <div class="team__content">
      <span class="team__tag">The Team</span>
      <h2>Meet Our Founders</h2>
      <p>
        Ana and Marko founded Dalmatia Estates with a shared vision: to showcase 
        Croatia's beauty through exceptional hospitality. With backgrounds in 
        architecture and luxury hospitality, they bring a unique perspective to 
        every property in our collection.
      </p>
      <blockquote>
        "We don't just rent villas. We create the backdrop for life's most precious moments."
        <cite>— Ana Horvat, Co-Founder</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
    <div class="team__image">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf?w=800&q=85&auto=format" alt="Our team" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="stats-section">
    <div class="stats-section__grid">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-item__num">48</span>
        <span class="stat-item__label">Curated Estates</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-item__num">12</span>
        <span class="stat-item__label">Years of Excellence</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-item__num">5,000+</span>
        <span class="stat-item__label">Happy Guests</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-item__num">98%</span>
        <span class="stat-item__label">Return Rate</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to experience Croatian luxury?</h2>
    <p>Let us help you find the perfect estate for your next escape.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Get in Touch</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    padding: 100px 5%;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .about-intro__image {
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .about-intro__image img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .about-intro__content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 44px);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  
  .about-intro__content h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--olive);
  }
  
  .about-intro__content p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--charcoal-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  .values {
    padding: 100px 5%;
    background: var(--linen);
  }
  
  .values__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  
  .values__tag {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--olive);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .values__header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 44px);
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  
  .values__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .value {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 24px;
  }
  
  .value__num {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    color: var(--sand);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  .value h3 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  
  .value p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--charcoal-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .team {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    padding: 100px 5%;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .team__tag {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--olive);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .team__content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 44px);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  
  .team__content p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--charcoal-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  
  .team__content blockquote {
    padding-left: 24px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--olive);
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  
  .team__content cite {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--stone);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  
  .team__image {
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .team__image img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .stats-section {
    padding: 100px 5%;
    background: var(--olive);
  }
  
  .stats-section__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .stat-item__num {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 64px);
    color: var(--cream);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  
  .stat-item__label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--sand);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    padding: 120px 5%;
    background: var(--cream);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  
  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--charcoal-light);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .values__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .team { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .stats-section__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-intro { padding: 60px 5%; }
    .values { padding: 60px 5%; }
    .values__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .team { padding: 60px 5%; }
    .stats-section { padding: 60px 5%; }
    .stats-section__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 40px 20px; }
    .cta-section { padding: 80px 5%; }
  }
</style>
